V0211_01_00_00_0.text: I'll begin the ritual to raise the King of the Netherworld!

V0211_01_00_01_0.text: I will become all-powerful and rule the world!

V0211_01_00_01_1.text: When the Crimson Dragon and the Netherworld both serve me!

V0211_01_00_02_0.text: Your sacrifice will bring the Netherworld to this realm!

V0211_01_00_02_1.text: Only by destroying this world can I rebuild it from scratch!

V0211_01_00_03_0.text: I’ll use the King of the Netherworld to lay waste to all!

V0211_01_00_03_1.text: Then have the Crimson Dragon rebuild the world in my image!

V0211_01_00_04_0.text: I can overcome the limits of humanity to change destiny!

V0211_01_00_04_1.text: And my name will become synonymous with miracles!

V0211_01_00_05_0.text: Where my brother failed, I will not.

V0211_01_00_05_1.text: I will change the course of destiny!

V0211_03_00_01_0.text: Don't you realize how powerless you are?

V0211_03_00_04_0.text: This must be some kind of a joke!

V0211_05_00_00_0.text: Where are your friends to help you now?

V0211_06_01_00_0.text: I won't let you do that!

I use my Continuous Trap!
Ultimate Earthbound Immortal!

V0211_08_00_18_1.text: I activate the Counter Trap, Divine Wrath!

V0211_08_00_20_0.text: You can't do anything without my permission!

V0211_09_00_01_0.text: I banish a Tuner from my Graveyard to Special Summon this!

V0211_09_00_08_1.text: And no one can stop this cycle!

V0211_09_00_09_0.text: By attacking Quilla, half your monster's ATK become my LP!

Greater Linewalker's effect activates!
Your LP become 3000!

V0211_09_00_21_1.text: Beckon my monsters from the beyond!

V0211_09_00_22_0.text: Guiding Light can revive a Level 1 LIGHT monster!

V0211_09_00_23_0.text: This card returns as a Tuner in Defense Position!

V0211_37_00_00_0.text: When the sun rises, its rays dissolve all the darkness!

V0211_37_00_01_0.text: As the moon rises, the whispers invite you to your end!

V0211_13_00_10_0.text: The mightiest Earthbound Immortal will rain destruction!

V0211_13_00_11_0.text: Souls are a small sacrifice to ensure its arrival!

V0211_13_00_12_0.text: Every sacrifice brings a new dawn!

V0211_13_00_13_0.text: I offer every soul on this planet to you!

V0211_13_00_16_0.text: I give this world to you!

V0211_37_00_02_0.text: Control the spirits as you control the sky!

V0211_37_00_03_0.text: Fate and destiny are no longer a mystery!

V0211_37_00_03_1.text:
When millennia of knowledge come to light!
I Synchro Summon!

V0211_37_00_04_0.text: The source of all power emerges from the dimension of chaos!

V0211_37_00_04_1.text: Quench your thirst in this realm!

V0211_37_00_05_0.text: The beginning and the end are both under its control!

V0211_37_00_05_1.text: Watch as chaos materializes into its true form!

V0211_13_00_25_0.text: I Special Summon a Utchatzimime Token!

V0211_13_00_28_0.text: Illuminate my field, Black Rose Moonlight Dragon!

V0211_13_00_35_0.text: I Special Summon a Dark Soul Token!

V0211_16_00_00_0.text: Your Life Points are like a candle flickering in a storm!

Fire Ant Ascator!
Sink your mandibles!

V0211_19_00_15_1.text: Wrap them up in your web of destruction!

V0211_19_00_30_0.text: Attack, Beelze of the Diabolic Dragons!

V0211_19_00_31_0.text: Attack, Beelzeus of the Diabolic Dragons!

V0211_21_00_00_1.text: The Netherworld will soon take over the planet!

V0211_21_00_01_1.text: Do you sense your own defeat looming?

V0211_21_00_05_1.text: How dare you do this to me...

V0211_28_00_00_0.text:
You had no chance.
Destiny chose me to rebuild the world!

V0211_28_00_01_0.text: Your bonds of friendship are easily snapped!

V0211_28_00_02_1.text: And bear witness to a new world of my own design!

V0211_28_00_03_0.text: Only I have the power to face both the light and the dark!

V0211_28_00_04_0.text: Your hope is but an illusion.

V0211_28_00_04_1.text: All that awaits you is the loneliness of the Netherworld!

V0211_28_00_05_0.text: You call yourself a King, but you're nothing but a peon!

V0211_28_00_05_1.text: Only I shall rule the new world!

V0211_28_00_06_0.text:
Where did you learn to ride a Duel Runner?
Preschool?

V0211_28_00_06_1.text:
You're no Turbo Duelist!
You're not even a Duelist!

V0211_29_00_00_1.text: Am I not the chosen one?

V0211_29_00_01_0.text: How can you not understand that my way is the best way?

V0211_29_00_02_0.text: I'm the greatest... so how could I lose?

V0211_29_00_03_0.text:
Am I not good enough?
Am I to live forever as a failure?

V0211_33_00_00_0.text: I'll show you two of the greatest!

V0211_30_00_02_0.text: You're a Turbo Duelist without any wheels.

V0211_34_00_01_0.text: What is a King compared to the divine?

V0211_34_00_03_0.text: You think summoning a monster in defense will help you?

V0211_34_00_04_0.text: It's only natural that my strategy is the best!

V0211_34_00_05_0.text: Stop fighting against those better than you!

V0211_34_00_06_0.text: When cornered, everyone resorts to silly tactics.

V0211_35_00_01_0.text: The Crimson Dragon and Netherworld are both mine to command!

V0211_36_00_00_0.text: If you copy what I do, you'll win.

V0211_36_00_02_0.text:
Is this 3-on-1?
Are you betraying me?
